# sitges

Parsing HTML data with enlive and then save it in Sqlite DB in order to allow complex querying

## Usage

Tool to download and manipulate database of sitges festival movies.

Options
  --show, -s      Prints databse                                    
  --populate, -p  Download movie information and populate database. 
  --drop, -d      Drops database and create a new one.     

## Build

lein deps
lein compile
lein run --populate
lein run --show

## Interactive design (Emacs+Swank)

lein swank

(inside emacs) 
M-x slime-connect
> (load "sitges/core")
> (in-ns 'sitges.core)
> (-main "--show")


